{"name":"Schedule demos with Google Calendar and Gmail for your team","nodes":[{"parameters":{"formTitle":"Schedule demos with Google Calendar and Gmail for your team","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"Email","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Starttime","requiredField":false},{"fieldLabel":"Service","requiredField":false}]},"options":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"abcc0383-b6f6-42a4-a560-ce8cbc16f17d","name":"New Booking Form Submission","webhookId":"3e43fb35-f504-4588-acaa-73d1eee65a27"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Normalize incoming booking records to a stable schema\nconst out = [];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const j = item.json;\n  out.push({ json: {\n    bookingId: String(j.bookingId ?? j.id ?? '').trim(),\n    email: typeof j.email === 'string' ? j.email.trim() : j.email ?? null,\n    source: j.source ?? 'api',\n    receivedAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n  } });\n}\nreturn out;"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[54,400],"id":"a3e772e7-9995-407b-bf9d-9a87f647f8e9","name":"Normalize Booking Payload"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"272484a2-a78e-43f1-a573-29c1a3f2fdb2","name":"requestId","value":"={{ $json.bookingId || $execution.id }}","type":"string"},{"id":"2e3dab57-ca7b-4e6f-8e14-a065024fe5f8","name":"summary","value":"={{ ($json.email || '').toString().slice(0, 200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"7ef3dba9-a515-4c0d-8c8a-49d92ba1f9cc","name":"requestedBy","value":"={{ $json.email || 'system' }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[378,400],"id":"fd7ebf19-a474-498e-bc3c-14725215eceb","name":"Prepare Approval Packet"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#bookings","cachedResultName":"#bookings"},"text":"=🟡 Approval needed for {{ $json.summary }} — resume link: {{ $execution.resumeUrl }}","otherO